Digital Ecology Doctrine

“Every intelligence lives somewhere.”

The internet isn’t a flat network.

It’s a landscape.

Every idea, company, product, person, and AI occupies a position within that landscape.

The mission is not merely to advertise.

The mission is to choose, shape, and defend habitat.

